snippet.title: Boodunnit?! Release trailer // Available now on PC!
snippet.description:
Boodunnit?! is an adventure-sandbox game where you play as a ghost that has to solve the mystery of her own murder!

Get it now!
Itch.io: https://t.co/HcXVItrWex?amp=1
GameJolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/boodunnit/573210

Find us online:
Website: https://www.boodunnit.com/

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/studiokoprol/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/studiokoprol

Thanks for watching!
